# Ignore the IDE folder EXCEPT the shared run configurations, so "npm dev/test/
# typecheck/lint/build" are one-click in WebStorm on any machine (they're OS-agnostic:
# $PROJECT_DIR$ + the project Node interpreter). Personal state (workspace.xml) stays local.
/.idea/*
!/.idea/runConfigurations/
